
Development map:

v0.1:

* Finish internal_osc branch, get back basic functionality with new
  class structure.  Includes:
  - Full set of joint types:
     . Prismatic and Rotoide
     . Prismatic - Universal
     . Plane 2D
  - Spring responses for all joints

v0.2:

* Re-implement extra functionality that was lost in the regression:
  - Textures
  - Composite objects
  - Mesh objects
  - Signal connections for Pd/Max version
  - More proxy information
  - Proxy object "grab"

v1.0:

* Allow run-time configuration of simulation synchroneity
* Embedded implementation of haptics thread for Toro DSP (Ergos)
* Process-oriented model
* Implement Introsca library to improve speed of inter-thread
  communication
* Support for libnifalcon
* More examples
